snippet.textDisplay:
I don't know what to say. It was a very lazy afternoon and I was just surfing the YouTube and just like any other song this came in the list and started playing. It was not more than a second when I suddenly heard Momina's voice and realize there's something in this song that attracts me so much. I actually listened to the song 5 times in the loop and there it was I was in love with the song and of course the singers. This song actually is a collab of two different songs Nawazishein Karam and Tera Woh Pyar. 
Nawazishein in one hand is as i came to know describes a hidden love story and Tera woh pyar as like other is a melodious song. Its actually the way these two singers presented the song that touched the pin point of my heart.
I really became a big fan of Momina and of course Asim Azhar. Its really beautiful and so romantic.
